=== Purchase Information === Product Title: 613 Blonde Virgin Hair Straight human hair 16 18 20 inch, Pack Of 3,100g/Bundle,Honey Blonde Brazilian Hair Weave,7A Blonde Human Hair boundles Review Date: 2017/05/08 Average Rating: 4.2 Product Details: {'Color': 'Honey blonde', 'Material': 'Human Hair', 'Extension Length': '20 Inches', 'Hair Type': 'Straight', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '10.7 x 6.1 x 2.9 inches; 1.15 Pounds', 'UPC': '712383517012'} Review Text: I have bought numerous extensions from different companies over the last 10 years, so I have plenty to compare these with. When I first opened the box, I was happy to see beautiful, soft hair! Nice and long, a little thin, but there are 3 bundles so you get quite a bit of hair. I usually have it put in by the sew in weave but I sewed clips on some of the pieces to try it first. It is thin, so I had to put 3 pieces on the clips. But very soft and silky! I tested some pieces by coloring, they got ratty very fast. The other pieces stayed fine for about 5-6 wearings, then also started to get tangled and bunched up. I never used shampoo to clean them, only lukewarm water with a heavy conditioner. I always took them out at night. Price was right but not sure about the quality. I have 1 1/2 of the bundle left and can't use. :( Review Title: Did not last Rating: 3.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Sunny Blonde Clip Hair Extensions 18 inch One Piece Clip in Human Hair Extensions Golden Blonde to Blonde Clip in Extensions Ombre Balayage Soft 70g Review Date: 2017/05/08 Store: Sunny Hair Average Rating: 4.0 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Sunny Hair', 'Material': 'Human Hair', 'Extension Length': '18 Inches', 'Hair Type': 'Straight', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Product Dimensions': '18 x 1 x 1 inches; 3.53 Ounces', 'UPC': '714973700828'} Review Text: At first was not to happy with this extension, it seemed too thin. The width should be a little more so it can come around each side of your head. So I tried adding pieces from another extension to make it more full. Also pulls on your hair, I think adding another clip or different positioning would help. But my head would be sore from the clips. The hair has stayed in pretty good shape. Beautiful color. I wear this once in a while if I'm in a hurry, I just don't add the other pieces so it looks a little thin. But overall, not a bad purchase for the money. Review Title: Still wearing Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: #18/613 Clip in 100% Remy Human Hair Extensions Double Weft 14''-22'' Grade 7A Quality Full Head Thick Long Soft Silky Straight 8pcs 18clips (18" / 18 inch 140g ,Light Ash Blonde/Bleach Blonde) Review Date: 2018/02/19 Average Rating: 3.7 Product Details: {'Material': 'Human', 'Extension Length': '14 Inches', 'Hair Type': 'Straight', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Installation Type': 'Clip-In', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '13.5 x 9.7 x 0.6 inches; 7.04 Ounces', 'UPC': '608912590413'} Review Text: The hair is very nice when first opened package. Soft and silky. However, after 2 weeks became dry and tangled. Should of lasted longer! Used a recommended conditioner for hair extensions but still lost the shine and it gets tangled up for easily. Review Title: One time use is all its good for. Rating: 2.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Full Shine Tape in Hair Extensions Real Human Hair Balayage Tape in Extensions Seamless Hair Extensions Ombre Glue in Hair Extensions Pu Tape Hair 50 Gram Review Date: 2018/03/14 Store: Full Shine Average Rating: 3.3 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Full Shine', 'Material': 'Human Hair', 'Extension Length': '24 Inches', 'Hair Type': 'Straight', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '9.53 x 5.12 x 1.42 inches; 1.76 Ounces', 'Item model number': '2016BALATP-50g-Nordic-24INCH', 'UPC': '614070317229'} Review Text: Soft shiny hair, beautiful color. One of the better companies to buy from. Will post another update after a few weeks to see how its holding up.
So, it's been almost 3 weeks, have washed with sulfate free shampoo and conditioner. Let it air dry and the first couple times it was still nice. The third time it seemed to need a boost so I used a hair mask overnite. Will last a few more weeks. Review Title: Very nice Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: 【9% Off】16inch Invisible Hair Extension Tape in Human Hair 50gram #16 Dark Ash Blonde Highlighted with #22 Golden Blonde Seamless Skin Weft Hair Extensions 20pcs Review Date: 2018/12/14 Average Rating: 1.0 Product Details: {'Material': 'Human', 'Hair Type': 'Wavy', 'Installation Type': 'Tape-In', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Product Dimensions': '15.98 x 0.98 x 0.98 inches; 5.28 Ounces', 'UPC': '716150455637'} Review Text: They looked awful just after wetting them down and of course after opening them they cant be returned. I dont understand all the good reviews unless I just happened to receive a bad one. They were ok until I sprayed just water on then to smooth the kinks from packaging. It must of washed off the coating. Review Title: Bad, very dry. Rating: 1.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Moresoo 18 Inch PU Tape in Hair Extensions Color #18 Ash Blonde Highlighted with #613 Blonde Invisible Seamless Skin Weft Human Hair Extensions Glue on 100g/40pcs Tape on Extensions Review Date: 2019/06/14 Average Rating: 3.9 Product Details: {'Material': 'Human Hair', 'Extension Length': '18 Inches', 'Hair Type': 'Straight', 'Installation Type': 'Glue-In, Tape-In', 'Is Discontinued By Manufacturer': 'No', 'Package Dimensions': '8.86 x 4.45 x 1.65 inches; 3.52 Ounces'} Review Text: Not very long lasting extensions, the hair got frizzy just wetting it down to remove the bend in hair from packaging. Although nice at first, a little thicker at the ends than most brands and as long as you brush thru it every couple hours you can keep the tangles at bay. But, will be replacing it as soon as possible, and have only had it in for about a week. Also trimmed the ends a couple of inches to see if that helped the frizzy look. It didn't. Bummer. Review Title: Lasts about a week or so. Rating: 2.0 --------------------------------------------------

raw_response:
SUMMARY:
This shopper demonstrates a consistent preference for human hair extensions, particularly in lighter shades like blonde and ombre styles. The average ratings across purchases reveal a sentiment leaning towards dissatisfaction regarding quality and longevity. Common themes include challenges with thinness, tangling, and overall durability of the hair. Critically, multiple reviews indicate a tendency toward purchasing clip-in and tape-in extensions, suggesting a preference for temporary, easy-to-manage styling options. 

Quality preferences emphasize the desire for softness and natural appearance; however, the shopper often notes that products fail to maintain these qualities post-use, indicating a significant concern regarding how well the extensions hold up over time. Price sensitivity is evident, with feedback reflecting a belief that while prices were reasonable, the quality did not justify the cost for several purchases. The shopper ultimately expresses disappointment when the products do not meet expectations, leading to high variability in ratings. Overall, the shopper's core preferences align with a need for affordable, visually appealing extensions, but they struggle to find products that withstand regular use without compromising on quality.
